%F A029332 a(n) = floor((n^3+36*n^2+236*n+2112)/6720 + n*((n mod 4)-2)^2/64 + ((n^3+n^2+n+2) mod 5)/5 + ((6*n^3+6*n^2+2*n+2) mod 7)/7). - _Hoang Xuan Thanh_, Apr 17 2026
